{"tid":317814,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[電腦爆炸]比部電腦電到啪啪聲","createTime":"2017-07-11T16:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T00:36:00.000Z","uid":31307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b69a1d2a7b2d4f32d44d95e3a4026a027b3f1cd","tid":317814,"uid":31307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:57:28.000Z","msg":"今日將部電腦主機由地下搬左上枱<br />\n用左一陣就俾張枱電到好多野<br />\n最後check到係部電腦主機個殼有電<br />\n原來一直以黎開左機 部主機都係漏電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家抆左個電制 個主機殼都仲係電親我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">接地係可以成功解決問題 但係成件事好麻煩</span><br />\n想問下個問題係出係邊度<br />\n<br />\n示意圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/005707_2d1cfa1f69de705a2968c6f877ca5c7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F005707_2d1cfa1f69de705a2968c6f877ca5c7d.jpg&h=874c3d39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40dad9d6a16370f24e61904b70490b75a0a865a4","tid":317814,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:00:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1084679d637de15b31e268154640c71757b2647","tid":317814,"uid":31307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知道左之後已經唔敢開機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日仲要諗下點樣搞先唔會比佢電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff8d9e0710c12640c7052e9086355ffb2d4bfa0","tid":317814,"uid":125895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"換過部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021a63693c465c2f58bf2adbb1c4f97a1383fc1e","tid":317814,"uid":31307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:11:35.000Z"